[{"Id": 1016420, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "The prayer mentioned in the book Najm-us-Saqib, narrated from the book of Syed Fazlullah Rawandi, under the title the prayer of our master Imam Mahdi (a). After offering the prayer, it is mentioned that one should recite Salawaat on Mohammad (s) and his Holy Progeny (a) 100 times. No other supplication has been mentioned after prayer and no specific time has been mentioned for the offering of this prayer.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Najm-us-Saaqib mein is namaz ko kitaab Syed Fazlullah Raawandi se yeh namaz Hazrat Imam-e-Zamana (a) ke oonwaan se naql kiya hai aur kaha hai namaz tamaam hone ke baad 100 martaba salawaat padhe lekin koi dua ka zikr nahi kiya hai aur farmaaya hai keh yeh namaz khaas zamaane ke saath makhsoos nahi hai.", "UrduDescription": "نجم الثاقب میں اس نماز کو کتاب سید فضل اللہ راوندی سے یہ نماز حضرت امام زمانہ کے عنوان سے نقل کیا ہے اور کہا ہے نماز تمام ہونے کے بعد ۱۰۰ مرتبہ درود بھیجے لیکن جس دعا کو میں نے ذکر کیا تھا اس کو بیان نہیں کیا ہے اور فرمایا ہے کہ یہ نماز خاص زمانہ کے ساتھ مخصوص نہیں ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "Arabi